{"tid":1304290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重整旗鼓】請各界聚焦真普選","createTime":"2019-07-10T14:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T05:46:38.000Z","uid":37528,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"21c7912be4f76fcbed14c2e8f80992c79ab0b558","tid":1304290,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"咁多個訴求柒婆都唔回應，應該將焦點聚焦去真普選，唔好洩左士氣<br />\n如果有普選，200萬人上街根本政府無可能唔落台<br />\n有普選，警權根本無可能過大<br />\n有普選，根本唔會有送中條例<br />\n有普選，2047香港先唔會變成中國<br />\n有普選，香港政府先會係服務市民而唔係服務中國<br />\n<br />\n贏一場小戰役但最後輸戰爭係無意思<br />\n民陣同各政黨可否聚焦番係真普選？<br />\n真普選係我地應得，英中聯合聲明講到明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170af417a8d3569bc85a40193d43d0cc27cc5cd2","tid":1304290,"uid":58958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"岩，真普通先解決到根源問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99ca9bf1059c795ce0d6929c8c458a49c10ce346","tid":1304290,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:37:43.000Z","msg":"拜託係7，8月既時候要focus係呢個訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf91f79add4fbcb51e319e879a8b72ceaf6f858","tid":1304290,"uid":37528,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"要保留士氣就唔好再注重係柒婆既字眼，佢夠膽再搞，我地就會再出黎<br />\n<br />\n呢個係好契機重啟政改(重有釋放義士都要繼續爭取)，美英加政府都有留意香港發生緊咩事<br />\n好難得先會有呢個天時地利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5387b2e3726a0e4691ca5edcc7de1002ccf77ca","tid":1304290,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"有意義討論post 推"},{"pid":"e8f2e2000124d9f137761220907bfbfc00503676","tid":1304290,"uid":258770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n要救香港唯一方法就係實施雙普選"},{"pid":"02b5debfb7c2c519da453c0f47e0ec64f1240e70","tid":1304290,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:44:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7410e3159cc7bd53f8ed120b384d66ac16a6127","tid":1304290,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:50:54.000Z","msg":"要各界都知道無普選根本對香港人無保障<br />\n今次只係中國侵佔香港其中一步棋，無普選，中國會繼續全面侵佔香港，佢地總有一次會成功<br />\n<br />\n大家開始吹風要爭取真普選啦唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0e299b06786de8ff5bb956488c7fa2463137bd","tid":1304290,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"外國都好關注香港民主壯況，彭斯仲見埋肥佬黎<br />\n香港人自己都要做好自己本分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01241fb1120b454dcb6b492de7d73e90bd73ec4","tid":1304290,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:55:28.000Z","msg":"建議民陣/其他團體：重力一擊應該留係每個月第一個假期<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1304338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1304338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點睇"},{"pid":"195c1b1375fba221890862f6448a10fc52943244","tid":1304290,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"f5522112fe21736de5e98532f7b082ba5f9c81bc","tid":1304290,"uid":240534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:56:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef1c2fb2f42c7fb79cb1792ba30d989c6092fefa","tid":1304290,"uid":258770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:06:53.000Z","msg":"推呀屌<br />\n唔好正係撤回就算 仲有好撚多中港銜接工程<br />\n無心搞革命推翻政府既就靠遊行爭取真雙普選<br />\n往後遊行既口號都唔該focus雙普選 有民選特首&amp;立法會先有足夠力量保護香港"},{"pid":"a6e6690fd367e05457a6c39c49653bc6e347db92","tid":1304290,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"目前戰線太多，運動重心稍為偏離；大家花太多時間係寶礦力同連儂場上面。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要集中火力係五大訴求上面。</span></span></strong>只有個議題仲係度，個運動先繼續有力量做其他野。重心要放返係「送中」上面，連帶反黑警；連儂場唔好太執著、反TVB唔好反多過林鄭。先搞「送中」，燈柱同信用評分先慢慢普及。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重心一定要放返係「送中」上面！<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聚焦五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連儂牆由得佢，第日再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2387482604810123%2Fposts%2F2908010702757308%3Fs%3D625469440%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3X4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=2ddfd8b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2387482604810123/posts/2908010702757308?s=625469440&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"97b5640d6ec0aebc3aecb3c46e93ba62b2d6bb3b","tid":1304290,"uid":276809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3455385a4c7377afda983076e08f9e714652f3","tid":1304290,"u